name: DPRK NFT(Democratic People's Republic of Korea) North Korea.
description: The base is made of red metal with an unusual texture. Cut from oxidized copper. The country is standing on a nuclear bomb that drives on rails with the help of a mechanism. The stand is made of white granite. Kim Jong-un, Chairman of the State Council of the DPRK, stands on a stand with a cigarette in his hand. On the reverse side of the stand, combat missiles are launched. The back of the stand is the emblem of the Workers ' Party of North Korea (the ruling party in the Democratic People's Republic of Korea).
